Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的风啊  传递我的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:20.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总是对你深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:29.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,那时站在梦里的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:37.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,环顾景色却有点望而却步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:45.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已决定头也不回的往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:54.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否也在仰望天空看那七色的彩虹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:01:02.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的风啊  传递我的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:11.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,守护着那朝着梦想前进的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:19.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,飞扬的风啊     追随着阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:29.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,挥着自由的翅膀勇敢地飞向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:36.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总是很自由的你 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:43.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨中追逐着怎样的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:48.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里与孤独作斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:54.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,强忍着眼泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:24:05.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也不要紧 你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:17.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然净是绕远路 为什么喜欢这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:23.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感到幸福 高兴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.07,0:24:29.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想起你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:35.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,色彩鲜艳的季节一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.43,0:24:42.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,传送这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去女子乔装就是打扮成男子的装束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为户部尚书的杂役
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽开始在外廷工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼过了十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小秀辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注：红秀丽女扮男装改名为红秀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点热没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这些公文按照日期排好并搬到府库去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的架子整理收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆那边的纸全部丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到府库把这些书借回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外归还这五本书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便把着封信送到鸿胪寺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:27.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,注：鸿胪寺为管理外宾接待以及朝贡之类事务的衙门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传话给那里的官员 竟然提出这么离谱的预算案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子一定生锈了  务必一字不漏传话过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:44.39,CH1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}千里之行 始于足下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么热的天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连男子都要甘拜下风的工作态度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实在的真令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前是贵妃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是自动装扮男子的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是过着充实的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 你也真是想得出这种不得了的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人手不足的户部...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是作为黄尚书身边的打杂人员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把秀丽小姐扔了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邵可大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来还书了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似一起带进来的燕青也被毫不客气地差遣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无比的能干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无比的怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都笼罩着迷一样的黄户部尚书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是秀丽小姐今年人生最大的坎坷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的一直提心吊胆地害怕何时被发现是女子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心啦放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绛攸大人不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以秀丽小姐的身材来说绝对不会被发现是女子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃...但是黄尚书是聪明的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定只把你看成是男子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自信是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？...呃...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐真是太有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么美味的饭菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝将军 绛攸大人总是麻烦你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请开怀多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐也大展才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 静兰打退山贼也消耗很多体力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃...好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作觉得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 每天都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心...吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绛攸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天饭后也请教我学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢指点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天的作业是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在国家的预算有剩余的情况下  你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望建立助产士与孕妇的补贴制度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设立奖励清寒学子就学的奖学金之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  而且可以作为改良耐灾害作物的研究经费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预算的用途有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如经费留着不花的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦紧急关头也不能拿来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为应该尽可能在需要时善加运用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和燕青去鸿胪寺把这些书卷返还
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个能干的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说了这么有建设性的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个月的临时人手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到鸿胪寺竟然是这幅惨状啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得会出那种不得了的计划书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种酷暑中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能正常使用大脑的也只有黄尚书这样人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴着面具难道不会热么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谣传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎绝对不会在人前摘下面具的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔戴着不同的面具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...到底有几个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种奇怪的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要戴面具呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因为那张脸的关系被女人甩掉的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是谣言呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具竟然是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏那张无法见容于世人的皮相吗...？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是人并非只有外表而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得黄尚书不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑聪明又有地位又有财富
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如当上他的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下半辈子就不愁吃穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一句才是你的真心话对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱可是很重要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从静兰这里接过保镖的工作真是太正确了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小姐在一起很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰今天也能平安回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过静兰有像燕青这样的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰有与人保持一定距离的习惯对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够结识跨越这条分界线的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐真是个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽！秀丽吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才感觉到秀丽气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是太热的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是动物般的嗅觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来蛮重的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你拿吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要搬到黄尚书大人那边对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说最近在黄尚书大人身边有个很勤奋的杂役就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫红…秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小秀啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄尚书大人是个很严格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我反而觉得学到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯   乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  小秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我这个人如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得您是一位好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您帮我搬书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,户部就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...请问您尊姓大名？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请叫我...大叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多好的称呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小秀——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为太热怪人就增多了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄尚书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是相当疲累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...头发好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇...真的好滑顺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...这该不会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红秀？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在发什么呆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回到阵营中去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 红秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是让我看到了有趣的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是好笑的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐是出名的怕打雷 我可是很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是一个人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 绝对被黄尚书讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是一到这个时候秀丽总是会没有精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外廷工作看来可以很好地转换心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有一个月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 只有一个月我也已经很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给勤快的公主送慰问品来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 以前曾想过当巡视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想当地方官吏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了很多事情...结果就...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再去参加不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 那我也和小姐一起学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绛攸大人可是非常地严厉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为一直做着不可能实现的梦的人是傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐的梦想是成为官吏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为小姐你每天晚上都这样勤奋努力到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外廷的工作也做得很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是不论怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女子是不能参加国试的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你是明知如此还这样努力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有什么样的梦想是个人的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊最近变得稍微接近点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为梦想和现实变的太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天在户部工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和梦想的交界线就变得非常的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也觉得好像是触手可及的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成大人后保持梦想就会变得很难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那样你也没有放弃吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 尽自己最大努力去做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千里之行始于足下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步虽说很小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总有一天会达成很大的目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐的话一定可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 多亏你我又有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燕青你就像新鲜空气一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白爹跟静兰之所以委托你前来的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来小姐早就发现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从饭团的捏法察觉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲的是奇形怪状的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大而圆 盐分又正好的是静兰的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为晚饭的时候说了奇怪的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小姐真是观察入微呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我觉得小姐很适合当官呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望小姐不要轻言放弃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 还要再努力下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在埋头苦干啊 真有毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是见不到秀丽虽有点寂寞...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想尽快让议案通过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从某种意义上来说是存在不纯动机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 这个世界男人和女人是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有男子的才能从政这种说法已经陈腐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对女性从政有意见这事已经蔓延到整个国家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我啊秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔啊 叫的真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她派到我这里的是你吗 红黎深
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 关于这件事你去问绛攸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了她的实际工作情况确实很勤快不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是明知她是女子还雇用她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为人手确实不够
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开放女子参加国试 根本是让人无法接受的荒唐提案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇上表示希望从下届开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就一语不发的离开于以否决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间太过仓促
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想改变只有男人才能从政的固有观念要花很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了女子参加 国试的制度也要有大幅的改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吏部的凌厉冷静冷酷又有才能的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反对的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个愚蠢的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天在看那个孩子的什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能通过国试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是前几名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绛攸也是这样保证的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撇开他是你的养子这点不说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李侍郎还真是顺应时代的卓越人才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后红秀如果不是你的侄女的话也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那个小女孩做我的新娘恐怕也不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 我绝对不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不是她的亲叔叔 没有反对的权利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新作品 接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我精心的力作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主题是 有点苦夏的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个 周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能感到连黄尚书也在苦夏真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而一定会增加亲近感的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 给我带回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...稍微休息一下的话怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少一天要喝一次茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人居然能老实地喝茶什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是晴天霹雳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来想当地中意你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 小秀你参加过国试没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少参加过一次左右吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这次国试一定要参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就能正式地加入户部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...听了你的话我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实我不能参加国试...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能参加？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚梨 高天凯与碧逊史倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于连他们两位也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天也马上就要过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再坚持一会就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...我们会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...是啊 如果是我们能做到的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起你兼任户部政务官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接任倒下的两个人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我待会儿再帮你写一张聘书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话可以做到吧 浪燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么到不了皇上的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明去过好几回了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会迷路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李侍郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是景侍郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上关于小秀我有事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道发现她是女的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给您添了什么麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有 其实真的工作得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄尚书好像也很中意他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 黄尚书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他很适合做官吏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我问过他 他说不能参加国试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真有什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意做他的担保人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景侍郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样说 小秀知道了肯定也会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却不能接受你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由的话到以后你就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当她成为官吏时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小秀他要参加国试？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那个时候我或者我的长官会担任他的担保人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 景侍郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在是要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...要把加急书信送到皇上那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也是的 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚也去打退山贼吗 燕青
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 而且被我们抓住的山贼们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都异口同声的说要找一个左脸颊有十字伤痕的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不要给老爷和小姐添麻烦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在想你真的被好人给捡回去了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐每晚都在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩变成夫妇就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着你的话不是什么都可以完美解决了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:23:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既能继续学习 也不会被周围催促快点结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想和性格那么坏的你一生都在一起的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那么多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每晚都去茶州抓贼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去向白大将军报告了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千里之行始于足下 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:55.54,CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}守得云开见月明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燕青到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.95,0:24:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留着杂乱的胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作能够做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像武功也很高
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:24:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被山贼袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.84,0:24:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
